GLMdenoise is a MATLAB toolbox developed by 
  Kendrick Kay, kendrick@post.harvard.edu, http://kendrickkay.net

To use the toolbox, add it to your MATLAB path:
  addpath(genpath('GLMdenoise'));

History of major code changes:
- 2012/11/03 - Initial version.

Example usage and example datasets:
- (coming soon)


